{{Infobox person | name = Alexandra Bech Gjørv | image = Konsernsjef Alexandra Bech Gjørv.jpg | alt = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = {{Birth year and age|1965}} | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | nationality = Norwegian | other_names = | parents = [[Toppen Bech]] | children = | relatives = [[Inger Lise Gjørv]] (mother-in-law) | occupation = Lawyer and businesswoman | years_active = | alma_mater = {{plainlist | *[[University of Oslo]] *[[University of Oxford]] *[[Suffolk University]] }} | known_for = | notable_works = [[Gjørv Report]] }} '''Alexandra Bech Gjørv''' (born 1965) is a Norwegian lawyer and businesswoman.
She is the daughter of journalist [[Toppen Bech]], and a daughter-in-law of politician [[Inger Lise Gjørv]]. She was assigned with [[Norsk Hydro]] from 1993 to 2007, and with [[Statoil]] from 2007 to 2010. She chaired the governmental commission appointed after the [[2011 Norway attacks]], which presented their findings in the [[Gjørv Report]].<ref name=snl>{{cite encyclopedia|title=Alexandra Bech Gjørv |first=Svein |last=Askheim |encyclopedia=[[Store norske leksikon]] |editor-last=Godal | editor-first=Anne Marit | editor-link=Anne Marit Godal |publisher=Norsk nettleksikon |location=Oslo |url=https://snl.no/Alexandra_Bech_Gjørv |language=Norwegian|accessdate=11 July 2016}}</ref> In 2015 she became the chief executive of [[SINTEF]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nrk.no/trondelag/gjorv-blir-ny-konsernsjef-i-sintef-1.12436270|title=Gjørv blir ny konsernsjef i SINTEF|last=Hustad|first=Helge Voll|date=1 July 2015|publisher=Norwegian Broadcasting Corporation|language=Norwegian|accessdate=12 July 2016}}</ref>
Gjørv graduated as [[cand.jur.]] in 1990 from the [[University of Oslo]], received further education at the [[University of Oxford]] (1991) and the [[Suffolk University]] in [[Boston]] (1993), and passed the New York State Bar Exam in 1994.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.sintef.no/en/alexandra-bech-gjorv/ |title=Alexandra Bech Gjørv, President and CEO |website=sintef.no |language=Norwegian |accessdate=20 October 2018 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hjort.no/webfiles/templates/emploees.aspx?id=3686&epslanguage=NO |title=Alexandra Bech Gjørv |website=hjort.no |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-09-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120910084242/http://www.hjort.no/webfiles/templates/emploees.aspx?id=3686&epslanguage=NO |language=Norwegian |accessdate=20 October 2018 }}</ref>
